The paper deals with visual reasoning tasks and proposes a conditioning method for neural networks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the effectiveness of the proposed method in improving the performance of deep learning models, which suggests that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
